### Fuel-Optimized Route Planner API
### API for calculating optimal fuel stops along routes

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Get Route (JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/route/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "Los Angeles, CA",
  "finish": "New York, NY"
}

### Get Route with Map (HTML)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/route/?format=map
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start": "Los Angeles, CA",
  "finish": "New York, NY"
}

### Chicago to Miami (Map)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/route/?format=map
